WEBVTT

01:32.130 --> 01:34.950
[How dare you!?]

01:35.009 --> 01:37.979
[Episode 5]

01:43.280 --> 01:44.610
We got the wrong person.

01:45.479 --> 01:46.509
It's a misunderstanding.

01:46.509 --> 01:48.000
It's all a misunderstanding.

01:48.000 --> 01:48.430
Sorry.

01:49.380 --> 01:50.240
Our apologies.

01:50.310 --> 01:51.310
Sorry about that.

02:00.350 --> 02:02.410
How dare you cause trouble on my turf?

02:02.680 --> 02:04.140
You must have a death wish.

02:31.190 --> 02:31.750
Dan.

02:36.079 --> 02:37.140
You really are Dan.

02:38.710 --> 02:40.440
-I...
-You really are Bei Zhou?

02:40.630 --> 02:41.750
Who is this girl?

02:42.650 --> 02:43.250
I'm his...

02:49.670 --> 02:51.070
I'm his favored consort,

02:51.680 --> 02:52.810
the love of his life,

02:53.400 --> 02:54.550
his one and only,

02:54.590 --> 02:55.870
the end of his journey,

02:56.590 --> 02:58.050
and the anchor of his soul,

02:58.840 --> 03:00.400
Yu Wanyin.

03:02.520 --> 03:03.520
Demonic consort.

03:06.360 --> 03:06.840
Dan.

03:10.680 --> 03:12.120
How did you know

03:12.840 --> 03:13.910
I was here?

03:15.760 --> 03:17.890
But isn't Bei Zhou supposed to be a man?

03:25.540 --> 03:26.000
Bei...

03:27.470 --> 03:29.130
Mrs. Bei, impressive skills.

03:29.280 --> 03:30.140
Mrs.?

04:03.680 --> 04:04.780
Right. This is it.

04:05.360 --> 04:07.020
We've found the right person.

04:07.680 --> 04:09.000
Bone-Constriction Skill?

04:09.000 --> 04:09.930
Disguise Art?

04:10.590 --> 04:12.320
Is this really the same person?

04:12.320 --> 04:13.050
Definitely.

04:13.630 --> 04:14.640
Look at his eyes.

04:15.470 --> 04:16.390
So bright,

04:17.120 --> 04:17.920
so beautiful,

04:18.950 --> 04:19.680
and so round—

04:20.200 --> 04:22.260
clearly not the eyes of a worker bee.

04:22.920 --> 04:23.720
So, Dan,

04:24.700 --> 04:26.360
how did you know

04:26.920 --> 04:28.250
someone like me exists?

04:28.300 --> 04:31.030
I've been away from the capital
for over a decade.

04:32.200 --> 04:33.260
That's because...

04:34.630 --> 04:35.270
Shut up.

04:38.270 --> 04:39.480
I'm asking Dan.

04:43.850 --> 04:44.560
This is bad.

04:45.000 --> 04:46.270
He's testing you.

04:46.930 --> 04:47.480
CEO Dan.

04:47.950 --> 04:49.150
Don't make things up.

05:01.740 --> 05:03.550
Of course I know about you, Mr. Bei,

05:03.550 --> 05:04.270
because...

05:04.270 --> 05:04.930
Because...

05:09.410 --> 05:11.620
Because I told him.

05:13.430 --> 05:14.960
Because you were mentioned

05:15.830 --> 05:17.430
in my mother's final letter.

05:19.440 --> 05:20.440
Gosh.

05:20.670 --> 05:22.600
You can actually explain it like that?

05:22.600 --> 05:23.890
Even the original novel
isn't as good as your story.

05:23.890 --> 05:25.550
How did Nan write about me?

05:26.870 --> 05:28.020
I know this one!

05:28.480 --> 05:30.540
Just be as melodramatic as possible.

05:30.600 --> 05:33.390
Something like "never once dreamed of
returning home for 10 years,"

05:33.390 --> 05:36.000
"longing for each other from afar
yet unrecognized,"

05:36.000 --> 05:39.240
or "vows remain,
but letters are hard to send."

05:39.320 --> 05:40.159
Mother said,

05:41.600 --> 05:43.330
"Dan, if you're ever in danger,

05:43.940 --> 05:45.940
the only person in the world to trust

05:46.920 --> 05:47.800
is Bei Zhou."

05:49.760 --> 05:51.560
You might as well just write
"Bei Zhou is useful"

05:51.560 --> 05:53.159
on your forehead.

06:07.690 --> 06:08.490
What?

06:08.890 --> 06:11.150
Those words actually moved him to tears?

06:13.100 --> 06:14.500
She still remembered me.

06:17.360 --> 06:18.310
Actually,

06:19.340 --> 06:20.940
since ascending the throne,

06:21.150 --> 06:23.480
I immediately sent people to look for you.

06:23.880 --> 06:25.080
Only after many years

06:25.800 --> 06:29.150
did we finally catch a faint trace of
your whereabouts, Mr. Bei.

06:29.150 --> 06:30.080
I came today

06:31.280 --> 06:32.620
merely to try my luck.

06:33.909 --> 06:34.840
I never expected

06:35.250 --> 06:36.710
to run into this incident.

06:37.620 --> 06:39.560
That man deserved to die.

06:41.370 --> 06:42.440
In his room,

06:42.800 --> 06:43.560
I found this.

06:50.430 --> 06:52.090
How can anyone read this?

06:55.570 --> 06:56.750
Reading so intently—

06:56.750 --> 06:58.750
do you even know the Qiang language?

07:04.030 --> 07:06.690
That man was an assassin
sent by the Qiang State?

07:07.430 --> 07:07.870
Dan,

07:08.430 --> 07:09.560
you are truly smart—

07:10.380 --> 07:11.740
just as smart as Nan.

07:13.190 --> 07:15.720
The Qiang State is wedged between
Yan and Xia.

07:15.870 --> 07:17.070
It's a mere speck of land,

07:17.070 --> 07:18.530
unable to protect itself,

07:18.560 --> 07:20.600
so it resorts to
underhanded assassinations,

07:20.600 --> 07:23.070
trying to stir up internal strife
in our state.

07:23.070 --> 07:24.670
But why did he want to kill me?

07:30.920 --> 07:31.870
Our probing just now

07:31.870 --> 07:33.470
might have made him think
his identity was exposed,

07:33.470 --> 07:34.920
so he tried to silence you.

07:34.920 --> 07:37.240
Or maybe these incompetents
you brought with you

07:37.240 --> 07:39.750
made him realize he'd already
blown his cover

07:39.750 --> 07:41.190
and that someone was coming after him.

07:41.190 --> 07:44.190
It seems the Qiang State
has been driven into a corner.

07:44.310 --> 07:44.800
Today,

07:45.870 --> 07:48.530
I'm fortunate to have been saved by you,
Mr. Bei.

07:48.800 --> 07:49.650
To be honest,

07:50.890 --> 07:52.350
my situation in the palace

07:54.140 --> 07:55.470
is indeed perilous now—

07:57.770 --> 07:58.830
beset on all sides.

08:00.480 --> 08:01.470
You really know how to put on an act.

08:01.470 --> 08:03.400
In truth, I returned to the capital

08:03.510 --> 08:05.770
for the sole purpose of keeping you safe.

08:06.000 --> 08:07.330
If I were to abandon you,

08:08.070 --> 08:09.200
in this whole world,

08:09.680 --> 08:10.610
who else could

08:10.830 --> 08:11.750
keep you safe?

08:13.480 --> 08:14.080
Mr. Bei...

08:14.920 --> 08:15.390
Dan...

08:15.870 --> 08:16.500
Mr. Bei...

08:17.190 --> 08:17.680
Dan...

08:18.360 --> 08:19.170
Mr. Bei!

08:22.680 --> 08:23.360
Dan...

08:27.360 --> 08:28.060
Auntie,

08:28.190 --> 08:30.670
why on earth are you leaving so suddenly?

08:30.870 --> 08:32.000
Where are you going?

08:32.020 --> 08:33.669
Could you please take me with you?

08:33.669 --> 08:36.030
-Let's leave together, Auntie.
-Take us with you.

08:36.030 --> 08:37.730
Given the current situation,

08:37.840 --> 08:40.039
should we call him Mr. Bei or Mrs. Bei?

08:40.070 --> 08:40.720
Auntie.

08:41.549 --> 08:42.610
Let's try them out.

08:43.830 --> 08:44.470
Mrs. Bei?

08:44.830 --> 08:45.370
Mr. Bei?

08:46.240 --> 08:47.640
Let's stick with Mr. Bei.

08:49.390 --> 08:50.440
Alright, alright.

08:50.440 --> 08:51.500
This is far enough.

08:51.720 --> 08:52.620
Go back now.

08:53.870 --> 08:57.070
-Come back soon, Auntie.
-Remember to come back, Auntie.

08:57.200 --> 08:57.790
Go back now.

08:57.790 --> 08:58.510
Auntie...

08:58.630 --> 08:59.080
Go back now.

08:59.080 --> 08:59.790
Auntie.

09:00.720 --> 09:01.770
Come back soon.

09:00.820 --> 09:04.180
[Banyue House]

09:02.030 --> 09:02.790
Auntie...

09:03.510 --> 09:04.440
I'll send people

09:04.670 --> 09:06.530
to look after Banyue House later.

09:06.600 --> 09:07.910
They won't be mistreated.

09:07.910 --> 09:08.440
Dan,

09:08.960 --> 09:10.090
you are so kind—

09:10.630 --> 09:11.630
just like Nan.

09:16.440 --> 09:16.900
Come on,

09:17.270 --> 09:17.710
Dan.

09:26.080 --> 09:26.630
Mr. Bei.

09:27.120 --> 09:29.780
Is this demonic consort
coming back with us too?

09:32.620 --> 09:33.570
Unfortunately,

09:34.000 --> 09:36.710
my home is right where your Dan lives.

09:47.250 --> 09:50.670
[Banyue House]

09:53.800 --> 09:57.220
[Banyue House]

10:02.000 --> 10:02.460
Mr. Bei,

10:03.150 --> 10:04.240
after we return to the palace,

10:04.240 --> 10:05.790
you won't need to wear a disguise anymore.

10:05.790 --> 10:06.990
Just pose as my guard.

10:07.150 --> 10:07.610
No need.

10:08.910 --> 10:10.390
I prefer the way I look now.

10:11.120 --> 10:13.390
Isn't it uncomfortable
wearing a disguise every day?

10:13.390 --> 10:14.120
Beauty

10:15.360 --> 10:16.960
always comes at a price.

10:24.050 --> 10:24.530
Mr. Bei,

10:25.960 --> 10:27.160
could you tell me more

10:27.600 --> 10:29.000
about your story with my mother?

10:29.000 --> 10:29.750
Nan

10:29.870 --> 10:32.670
was the only person in the world
who understood me.

10:33.120 --> 10:34.550
She never despised me.

10:35.000 --> 10:37.550
She taught me how to write poems

10:37.870 --> 10:39.280
and how to dress myself.

10:39.670 --> 10:41.080
I remember that back then,

10:41.080 --> 10:42.660
the first time I wore a bodice...

10:42.660 --> 10:43.120
Mr. Bei!

10:46.840 --> 10:47.970
You can write poems?

10:49.000 --> 10:50.660
Can you compose one right now?

10:54.090 --> 10:55.090
I was just joking.

10:55.600 --> 10:56.600
You don't have to.

10:57.080 --> 10:57.510
Sure.

11:06.120 --> 11:08.110
The moonlight is soft,

11:08.770 --> 11:09.910
like an egg.

11:14.630 --> 11:16.510
Crack it in a bowl,

11:17.670 --> 11:18.600
and it scatters.

11:20.790 --> 11:22.240
You call that a poem?

11:22.530 --> 11:24.540
[Zhaoyang Hall]

11:24.910 --> 11:27.000
You want me to stay in
this demonic consort's palace?

11:27.000 --> 11:28.440
It's the Noble Consort's Palace.

11:28.440 --> 11:30.120
I fear there are spies around me.

11:30.120 --> 11:32.080
The Noble Consort's Palace,
on the other hand, is sparsely staffed.

11:32.080 --> 11:33.480
It's easier to talk here.

11:33.600 --> 11:34.630
Easier to talk?

11:35.210 --> 11:37.370
[Zhaoyang Hall]

11:35.440 --> 11:37.520
Three on the roof, two in the side hall,

11:37.520 --> 11:39.850
one in the side room
and one in the kitchen.

11:41.120 --> 11:41.660
Great.

11:42.320 --> 11:43.690
Now all 7 men of ours

11:44.120 --> 11:45.520
are completely exposed.

11:46.090 --> 11:47.690
These are all our own people.

11:47.790 --> 11:48.390
It's fine.

11:59.670 --> 12:01.270
I earnestly ask you, Mr. Bei,

12:01.430 --> 12:02.090
to treat her

12:02.730 --> 12:03.730
as you'd treat me.

12:04.670 --> 12:06.800
Please ensure her safety at all costs.

12:07.830 --> 12:08.630
Rest assured.

12:09.670 --> 12:11.200
I'll definitely eliminate

12:11.320 --> 12:13.380
the traitors at Your Majesty's side.

12:20.080 --> 12:21.280
Three of Characters.

12:21.990 --> 12:24.590
[Minister Yu]

12:25.080 --> 12:25.840
Straight.

12:26.120 --> 12:26.910
Straight.

12:27.320 --> 12:27.840
I won.

12:28.480 --> 12:30.320
Come on, pay up.

12:31.390 --> 12:31.890
-Come on.
-Here.

12:31.890 --> 12:32.550
Here.

12:32.790 --> 12:33.390
Here.

12:33.720 --> 12:34.240
Master!

12:34.960 --> 12:35.420
Master!

12:35.750 --> 12:36.210
Master!

12:37.670 --> 12:38.800
Prince Duan is here.

12:39.870 --> 12:40.600
Prince Duan?

12:42.480 --> 12:43.940
What would bring him here?

12:44.320 --> 12:46.360
He says he's here to congratulate you—

12:46.360 --> 12:49.220
Consort Yu has just been elevated
to Noble Consort.

12:51.140 --> 12:51.600
Master.

12:52.390 --> 12:52.920
Noble...

12:53.360 --> 12:54.220
Noble Consort?

12:57.460 --> 12:59.190
I didn't know Your Highness...

13:00.910 --> 13:02.390
I didn't know Your Highness was coming.

13:02.390 --> 13:04.240
Please forgive me for not welcoming you

13:04.240 --> 13:05.720
properly, Your Highness.

13:06.270 --> 13:07.270
Vice Minister Yu,

13:07.600 --> 13:09.730
there is no need for such formalities.

13:10.120 --> 13:11.120
I just happened to

13:12.760 --> 13:13.500
be passing by

13:14.280 --> 13:17.010
and thought I'd share in
the Noble Consort's joy.

13:18.150 --> 13:19.010
Your Highness,

13:19.270 --> 13:20.200
you are too kind.

13:22.120 --> 13:22.630
I...

13:23.240 --> 13:25.370
Actually, I hadn't received any news.

13:29.240 --> 13:31.970
For such a big matter
as being made Noble Consort,

13:32.030 --> 13:33.550
she didn't even send word home?

13:33.550 --> 13:34.910
To be honest, Your Highness,

13:34.910 --> 13:37.310
ever since my daughter became a concubine,

13:37.960 --> 13:40.120
she hasn't contacted us.

13:43.670 --> 13:45.910
But I understand—

13:46.390 --> 13:48.920
after all, it's not appropriate
for the harem

13:49.240 --> 13:50.000
to interact too much

13:50.000 --> 13:51.730
with their original families.

13:54.080 --> 13:55.140
Well, that is true.

13:56.840 --> 13:59.640
Lord Yu, you have truly
raised your daughter well.

14:00.080 --> 14:01.510
Not only is Noble Consort Yu

14:01.510 --> 14:03.040
exceptionally beautiful,

14:04.080 --> 14:07.340
I've also heard she's highly accomplished
in her studies.

14:10.370 --> 14:12.320
It just so happens that
I have a close friend

14:12.320 --> 14:13.780
whose daughter has always

14:13.910 --> 14:16.370
looked up to Noble Consort Yu
as a role model.

14:18.360 --> 14:19.580
So I'd like to

14:20.390 --> 14:21.650
ask you for a favor:

14:22.600 --> 14:25.290
please select one of
Consort Yu's calligraphy or paintings

14:25.290 --> 14:26.420
to give her as a gift.

14:27.960 --> 14:30.000
Of... Of course, why not?

14:31.720 --> 14:32.080
Fu.

14:32.870 --> 14:34.710
Hurry and bring one of

14:34.870 --> 14:35.870
Lady Yu's calligraphy or paintings.

14:35.870 --> 14:36.330
Master.

14:36.630 --> 14:38.320
Her Highness sent someone a few days ago

14:38.320 --> 14:40.380
to take all her works into the palace.

14:41.270 --> 14:41.840
That day,

14:42.870 --> 14:43.870
you weren't here.

14:46.080 --> 14:46.910
Your Highness,

14:46.910 --> 14:49.080
you see, I didn't know.

14:51.030 --> 14:51.830
But it's okay.

14:52.550 --> 14:55.240
I taught my daughter everything
she knows about calligraphy and painting.

14:55.240 --> 14:56.440
I can write something for you.

14:56.440 --> 14:57.000
Lord Yu.

14:59.630 --> 15:00.510
It's okay. Forget it.

15:00.510 --> 15:01.770
Please don't say that.

15:01.790 --> 15:03.850
I'll be quick. Just a moment, please.

15:20.440 --> 15:21.720
The stronger a person is,

15:21.720 --> 15:23.650
the more they prefer to work alone—

15:24.440 --> 15:25.440
even on missions,

15:26.320 --> 15:28.050
they don't bring anyone along.

15:28.270 --> 15:28.720
What?

15:30.120 --> 15:30.600
Mr. Bei

15:30.960 --> 15:32.380
has gone to Prince Duan's Mansion
to get the book?

15:32.380 --> 15:33.180
That's right.

15:34.720 --> 15:36.140
Isn't that too rushed?

15:36.910 --> 15:37.980
Xu Yao told us

15:38.870 --> 15:40.120
to wait a bit

15:40.840 --> 15:42.570
so we wouldn't alert the enemy.

15:42.870 --> 15:43.270
I'm worried that...

15:43.270 --> 15:44.980
I know what you're worried about.

15:44.980 --> 15:46.280
Xiahou Bo

15:46.360 --> 15:48.630
has been scheming painstakingly for years,

15:48.630 --> 15:49.460
and his mind is

15:50.080 --> 15:51.550
exceedingly dark and sinister.

15:51.550 --> 15:52.480
Prince Duan's Mansion

15:52.480 --> 15:53.880
must be heavily guarded.

15:53.960 --> 15:55.820
But Mr. Bei is no ordinary person.

15:55.870 --> 15:56.840
You said it yourself that

15:56.840 --> 15:59.270
he has the highest combat power
in the entire book.

15:59.270 --> 16:00.670
Even if there's trouble,

16:01.150 --> 16:02.280
with his abilities,

16:02.630 --> 16:03.360
I believe

16:05.240 --> 16:06.970
he can turn it to his advantage.

16:10.240 --> 16:10.970
That's true.

16:13.960 --> 16:16.290
Now that we have
the book Xu Yao left behind

16:17.200 --> 16:19.200
and know all of Prince Duan's plans,

16:19.240 --> 16:20.640
can we really defeat him?

16:20.720 --> 16:23.600
How much that book can actually
help us is another matter.

16:23.600 --> 16:24.200
So for now,

16:25.510 --> 16:27.150
don't overthink it.

16:29.670 --> 16:31.120
I understand the logic,

16:32.430 --> 16:34.270
but ever since we transmigrated here,

16:34.270 --> 16:36.130
so many plot points have changed.

16:36.440 --> 16:37.970
I really can't feel at ease.

16:39.750 --> 16:41.550
Besides, in the original story,

16:42.780 --> 16:44.420
Xu Yao lived for a long time.

16:45.870 --> 16:47.000
Don't worry.

16:47.480 --> 16:49.000
The worst that could happen

16:49.000 --> 16:50.030
is we die.

16:54.200 --> 16:55.090
Thanks.

16:55.440 --> 16:56.900
That's oddly comforting.

17:11.829 --> 17:13.200
Why is he so handsome?

17:16.270 --> 17:18.400
I've never seen him trim his eyebrows.

17:19.589 --> 17:20.790
So why are they shaped

17:21.000 --> 17:22.440
so perfectly?

17:23.829 --> 17:24.750
His eyes,

17:25.109 --> 17:25.790
nose,

17:26.440 --> 17:27.040
and mouth.

17:37.480 --> 17:39.140
My dear, are you peeking at me?

17:41.790 --> 17:42.270
No.

17:43.270 --> 17:44.320
Who's peeking?

17:44.400 --> 17:46.600
I... I was worried about your headache.

17:46.880 --> 17:48.410
I'm going to take a bath now.

17:51.660 --> 17:52.660
Why not together?

17:53.270 --> 17:54.470
You can see even more.

17:55.720 --> 17:56.850
How inappropriate!

18:44.640 --> 18:45.510
My dear,

18:46.200 --> 18:47.400
are you peeking at me?

18:49.730 --> 18:51.060
Stop thinking about it.

18:52.540 --> 18:54.310
Being love-struck is a huge taboo.

18:54.310 --> 18:55.200
In stories like this...

18:55.200 --> 18:57.720
-Why not together?
-The love-struck all die young.

18:57.720 --> 18:59.580
What's wrong with you, Yu Wanyin?

19:00.110 --> 19:01.440
In this food chain,

19:01.840 --> 19:03.440
you are already the weakest.

19:03.510 --> 19:04.830
If you want to survive till the end,

19:04.830 --> 19:06.670
you can't let primal urges conquer you.

19:06.670 --> 19:07.800
Stay clear-headed.

19:09.550 --> 19:10.410
Clear-headed.

19:11.830 --> 19:12.830
Stay clear-headed.

19:12.830 --> 19:13.960
Stay clear-headed.

19:18.750 --> 19:20.830
How can I stay clear-headed?

19:30.110 --> 19:31.750
Please take a look, Your Majesty.

19:31.750 --> 19:32.880
Is this from Mr. Bai?

19:34.070 --> 19:34.400
Yes.

19:57.400 --> 19:58.070
Tell him

19:58.720 --> 20:00.480
that everything in the palace is as usual

20:00.480 --> 20:02.610
and that he should proceed as planned.

20:03.510 --> 20:03.930
Yes.

20:15.530 --> 20:19.230
[The demonic consort is ominous
and must be eliminated immediately]

20:41.400 --> 20:41.790
You

20:42.200 --> 20:43.800
finished washing up so soon?

20:45.550 --> 20:46.550
You were slow.

21:22.070 --> 21:23.200
Can't sleep either?

21:25.350 --> 21:26.680
I knew it wouldn't work.

21:30.480 --> 21:31.280
What's wrong?

21:32.400 --> 21:33.000
Headache.

21:34.550 --> 21:35.010
Then...

21:35.750 --> 21:37.680
Do you want me to give you a massage?

21:39.310 --> 21:41.960
I-I'm just showing humanitarian concern.

21:40.360 --> 21:42.360
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

21:42.640 --> 21:44.070
It's perfectly normal
to care about a companion.

21:42.730 --> 21:43.980
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

21:44.310 --> 21:46.410
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

21:46.830 --> 21:48.150
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

21:48.240 --> 21:50.650
♪ Words unspoken ♪

21:52.190 --> 21:54.630
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

21:56.300 --> 21:58.440
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

21:58.760 --> 21:59.860
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

21:59.000 --> 21:59.930
I'll be gentler.

22:00.260 --> 22:02.260
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

22:02.760 --> 22:04.140
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

22:03.920 --> 22:06.160
I don't know if you'll find this
comforting,

22:04.350 --> 22:06.680
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

22:08.200 --> 22:11.540
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

22:08.720 --> 22:11.720
but the headache is just part of
your character setting.

22:11.720 --> 22:13.310
You didn't end up dying from it anyway.

22:12.160 --> 22:15.530
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

22:14.200 --> 22:14.750
At least,

22:15.110 --> 22:16.510
before you were assassinated,

22:16.300 --> 22:19.260
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

22:17.070 --> 22:18.330
you didn't die from it.

22:19.640 --> 22:20.640
Thanks.

22:19.790 --> 22:21.580
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

22:21.550 --> 22:22.510
That's oddly comforting.

22:21.820 --> 22:23.460
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

22:23.770 --> 22:25.460
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

22:25.680 --> 22:27.860
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

22:28.070 --> 22:28.830
Later,

22:28.310 --> 22:31.360
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

22:29.720 --> 22:31.310
have Mr. Bei examine you

22:32.270 --> 22:34.610
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

22:32.880 --> 22:34.730
and see if it's a brain tumor or poison.

22:34.730 --> 22:35.870
♪ Still unchanged ♪

22:36.000 --> 22:37.790
Mr. Bei is experienced
in the martial world.

22:36.270 --> 22:39.140
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

22:38.550 --> 22:40.070
He might know of some poisons

22:39.850 --> 22:41.210
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

22:40.070 --> 22:41.340
that even the imperial physicians
have never heard of.

22:41.340 --> 22:45.470
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

22:50.480 --> 22:52.940
You're actually afraid of death too,
right?

22:55.240 --> 22:55.900
Hard to say.

23:00.070 --> 23:00.960
It's okay.

23:02.030 --> 23:02.680
I'm afraid too.

23:02.350 --> 23:04.420
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

23:04.160 --> 23:06.480
But as a CEO,
you need to adjust your mindset.

23:04.700 --> 23:05.940
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

23:06.290 --> 23:08.450
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

23:06.790 --> 23:07.790
Show some spirit.

23:08.810 --> 23:10.190
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

23:09.000 --> 23:10.080
Even if Mr. Bei

23:10.280 --> 23:12.580
♪ Words unspoken ♪

23:10.960 --> 23:12.490
couldn't get the book back,

23:12.960 --> 23:14.200
-we can still fight again...
-Don't worry.

23:14.200 --> 23:16.580
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

23:18.310 --> 23:20.400
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

23:19.590 --> 23:20.800
As long as you don't want to give up,

23:20.800 --> 23:21.890
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

23:22.250 --> 23:23.240
I won't give up either.

23:22.340 --> 23:24.260
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

23:24.820 --> 23:26.150
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

23:26.280 --> 23:28.690
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

23:30.280 --> 23:33.720
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

23:34.170 --> 23:37.670
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

23:37.880 --> 23:40.030
After all, I'm counting on you
to lead me to a good life, Wanyin.

23:38.240 --> 23:41.240
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

23:41.700 --> 23:43.630
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

23:43.830 --> 23:45.430
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

23:45.770 --> 23:47.380
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

23:46.030 --> 23:46.880
That's true.

23:47.780 --> 23:49.880
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

23:50.300 --> 23:53.460
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

23:54.250 --> 23:56.660
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

23:56.730 --> 23:57.790
♪ Still unchanged ♪

23:57.880 --> 23:58.680
I'm going to sleep.

23:58.340 --> 24:01.200
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

23:59.160 --> 23:59.820
Good night.

24:01.800 --> 24:03.250
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

24:02.510 --> 24:03.170
Good night.

24:03.360 --> 24:07.900
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

24:22.170 --> 24:25.700
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

24:26.240 --> 24:29.240
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

24:27.310 --> 24:29.110
Even if she's a demonic consort,

24:29.590 --> 24:30.680
she's a good-looking one.

24:29.780 --> 24:31.630
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

24:31.850 --> 24:33.530
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

24:33.830 --> 24:35.500
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

24:35.790 --> 24:37.950
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

24:38.330 --> 24:41.510
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

24:42.310 --> 24:44.720
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

24:44.820 --> 24:49.070
[Zhaoyang Hall]

24:44.840 --> 24:45.890
♪ Still unchanged ♪

24:46.350 --> 24:49.260
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

24:49.810 --> 24:51.260
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

24:51.320 --> 24:58.690
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

25:17.110 --> 25:17.880
Wake up.

25:18.200 --> 25:19.130
The book is here.

25:23.830 --> 25:24.630
Your Majesty.

25:25.200 --> 25:26.270
Grand Tutor Wei

25:27.000 --> 25:29.130
hanged himself in his cell last night.

25:33.350 --> 25:34.880
That saves me some trouble.

25:36.960 --> 25:41.160
Grand Tutor Wei was a smart man, you know.

25:42.440 --> 25:43.440
How did he end up having

25:43.440 --> 25:45.850
such useless children?

25:48.240 --> 25:49.680
Poor Grand Tutor Wei.

25:50.830 --> 25:53.960
In the end, to protect them,

25:54.440 --> 25:57.590
he ruined his reputation

25:58.240 --> 26:00.770
by committing suicide
to escape punishment.

26:01.880 --> 26:02.680
Your Majesty,

26:03.160 --> 26:04.560
as for Noble Consort Wei,

26:04.920 --> 26:06.250
are we still going to...

26:07.550 --> 26:10.000
No love is as selfless as parents' love.

26:11.640 --> 26:14.030
Let her stay in the Cold Palace

26:14.510 --> 26:15.910
until she dies of old age.

26:15.960 --> 26:16.310
Yes.

26:17.640 --> 26:18.400
Yesterday,

26:19.000 --> 26:20.660
who served the Emperor in bed?

26:21.310 --> 26:22.110
Your Majesty,

26:22.920 --> 26:24.160
last night, His Majesty

26:24.160 --> 26:26.200
stayed with Noble Consort Yu again.

26:29.830 --> 26:31.160
Did they sleep together?

26:31.160 --> 26:32.830
The Noble Consort's Palace
is heavily guarded.

26:32.830 --> 26:33.760
It's hard to spy.

26:34.350 --> 26:36.830
Besides, His Majesty usually
dismisses the servants

26:36.830 --> 26:38.690
to be alone with Noble Consort Yu.

26:38.790 --> 26:40.400
As for whether they slept together,

26:40.400 --> 26:42.260
there's really no way to find out.

26:45.920 --> 26:49.580
In the harem, the worst thing
is one faction growing too dominant.

26:50.640 --> 26:52.720
Before, Noble Consort Wei

26:53.350 --> 26:55.440
could keep her somewhat in check,

26:58.440 --> 26:59.570
but now, Yu Wanyin's

27:00.480 --> 27:02.640
influence is growing too strong.

27:03.480 --> 27:05.340
It's time to dampen her momentum.

27:06.510 --> 27:08.120
What rank is her father?

27:08.590 --> 27:09.390
Your Majesty,

27:09.720 --> 27:11.240
he's a fourth-rank official.

27:11.240 --> 27:13.340
A lowly Vice Minister.

27:13.550 --> 27:14.350
That's right.

27:15.310 --> 27:16.070
Very well.

27:16.720 --> 27:18.270
I'll make her understand

27:18.750 --> 27:20.750
that in this harem,

27:21.270 --> 27:24.680
there's no room for a girl like her

27:25.000 --> 27:27.070
to run amok.

27:31.280 --> 27:36.500
[Zhaoyang Hall]

27:32.270 --> 27:33.510
Zhaoyang Palace

27:33.590 --> 27:36.990
was specially bestowed upon
Noble Consort Yu by His Majesty.

27:37.030 --> 27:39.720
His Majesty worries that
you young servants

27:39.720 --> 27:40.880
won't serve well,

27:41.720 --> 27:44.110
so he specially found someone experienced

27:44.110 --> 27:45.910
to supervise the daily routine.

27:46.310 --> 27:46.920
Please.

28:16.720 --> 28:18.960
You can call me...

28:20.480 --> 28:21.350
Madam Bei.

28:22.720 --> 28:23.400
Yes.

28:24.880 --> 28:25.640
Madam here

28:26.030 --> 28:28.360
used to serve the former Empress Dowager.

28:28.510 --> 28:31.170
Keep your eyes wide open
and learn well from her.

28:32.270 --> 28:33.200
Do you hear me?

28:33.270 --> 28:37.490
[Zhaoyang Hall]

28:33.680 --> 28:34.400
Yes.

28:36.110 --> 28:37.640
Her Highness prefers quiet

28:37.750 --> 28:39.680
and stays deep within her chambers.

28:39.680 --> 28:40.710
Except for me,

28:41.480 --> 28:42.160
Mei,

28:42.240 --> 28:43.360
all other maids

28:43.510 --> 28:44.910
are not allowed to enter.

28:45.680 --> 28:46.310
Yes.

28:47.240 --> 28:47.770
Alright.

28:48.310 --> 28:49.970
All of you may get back to work.

28:52.960 --> 28:54.920
Thank you for your trouble, Eunuch An.

28:54.920 --> 28:55.880
Not at all.

28:56.480 --> 28:58.480
We are all here to serve our masters.

28:58.750 --> 29:00.400
Since His Majesty ordered it,

29:00.400 --> 29:02.830
we servants just need to do our best.

29:03.390 --> 29:03.820
Yes.

29:06.590 --> 29:07.390
Leave it to me.

29:07.790 --> 29:08.790
I am Mei.

29:09.640 --> 29:11.030
Didn't you just say

29:11.270 --> 29:12.200
"except for me?"

29:12.400 --> 29:13.680
I said "except for me,

29:14.480 --> 29:15.920
Mei, all other maids

29:16.030 --> 29:17.490
are not allowed to enter."

29:18.350 --> 29:20.430
She meant Mei and all other maids,

29:20.590 --> 29:22.450
-including you.
-Including you.

29:22.830 --> 29:23.680
Just listen to Madam Bei.

29:23.680 --> 29:24.410
Hand it over.

29:26.790 --> 29:28.640
His Majesty has arrived!

29:37.680 --> 29:39.680
No need for such formalities, Mr...

29:41.680 --> 29:42.280
Madam Bei?

29:44.250 --> 29:45.250
W-What's wrong?

29:47.040 --> 29:48.760
Is my makeup

29:49.920 --> 29:50.920
not fancy enough?

29:52.130 --> 29:52.880
I just entered the palace,

29:52.880 --> 29:54.530
and I don't know the rules.

29:54.720 --> 29:56.160
Is it a bit too plain?

29:59.960 --> 30:02.690
Ask Wanyin to help you
adjust it a bit another day.

30:04.240 --> 30:05.590
I left in a hurry this morning,

30:05.590 --> 30:06.790
so I didn't get to ask.

30:07.400 --> 30:08.750
Regarding the trip last night,

30:08.750 --> 30:10.550
you didn't encounter any difficulties,
did you?

30:10.550 --> 30:11.410
Difficulties?

30:12.350 --> 30:16.680
"The item is 1 meter below the window of
the Prince Duan's Mansion's kitchen."

30:19.500 --> 30:21.160
There are so many windows in the kitchen.

30:21.160 --> 30:22.110
Which one is it?

30:24.270 --> 30:24.730
Mr. Bei?

30:26.030 --> 30:27.550
At Prince Duan's Mansion last night,

30:27.550 --> 30:29.070
did you encounter any difficulties?

30:29.070 --> 30:29.730
Not at all.

30:29.960 --> 30:31.910
It was a piece of cake.

30:42.550 --> 30:43.640
He didn't even make it clear

30:43.640 --> 30:44.790
which window it is.

30:46.290 --> 30:48.610
[Ways to win over Deputy Commander Zhao]

30:47.790 --> 30:48.720
I see.

30:49.590 --> 30:49.960
So...

30:53.400 --> 30:54.680
So that explains it.

30:58.960 --> 31:00.200
-Dan, look.
-I see.

31:03.640 --> 31:04.640
That's not right.

31:04.750 --> 31:06.310
Ever since she opened this booklet,

31:06.310 --> 31:08.240
-she's been acting jumpy.
-This...

31:08.240 --> 31:09.960
Even when I spoke to her,
she wouldn't respond.

31:09.960 --> 31:12.290
-Why is she like this?
-What is this thing?

31:15.640 --> 31:17.030
What does this mean?

31:22.920 --> 31:23.650
You're here.

31:24.310 --> 31:26.200
I happen to have something to ask you.

31:26.200 --> 31:26.820
Look at this.

31:26.820 --> 31:28.160
[Ways to win over Deputy Commander Zhao]

31:27.240 --> 31:28.370
"Turn Deputy Zhao."

31:28.680 --> 31:29.740
Who is Deputy Zhao?

31:31.030 --> 31:33.550
There is indeed a Deputy Commander
surnamed Zhao in the Imperial Guards.

31:33.550 --> 31:34.270
Could it be him?

31:34.270 --> 31:35.270
That explains it!

31:35.310 --> 31:36.170
Explains what?

31:36.310 --> 31:38.370
What exactly is written in this book?

31:39.000 --> 31:40.160
This book records

31:40.160 --> 31:41.680
Prince Duan's future plans.

31:41.680 --> 31:42.810
"Turn Deputy Zhao."

31:43.350 --> 31:44.410
It basically means

31:44.450 --> 31:46.830
he wants to turn Deputy Commander Zhao
of the Imperial Guards,

31:46.830 --> 31:48.350
make him the Commander,

31:49.110 --> 31:51.160
and thereby bring
the Imperial Guards' power

31:51.160 --> 31:52.400
under his own control.

31:52.400 --> 31:55.480
Aren't the Imperial Guards supposed to
protect the Imperial City?

31:55.480 --> 31:57.540
If Prince Duan wants to control them,

31:57.680 --> 31:58.810
what is he planning?

31:59.880 --> 32:00.640
Exactly.

32:01.550 --> 32:02.530
Why do I remember

32:02.720 --> 32:04.890
this wasn't part of the original story?

32:04.890 --> 32:06.350
Where did it go wrong?

32:10.400 --> 32:11.930
Why are you two acting so...

32:20.210 --> 32:22.020
Isn't he planning a rebellion?

32:22.240 --> 32:22.770
Correct.

32:24.110 --> 32:25.710
But now that we have the book,

32:26.470 --> 32:28.300
we can defeat them one by one

32:28.920 --> 32:29.720
and make their

32:30.310 --> 32:31.270
plans fail.

32:32.510 --> 32:33.770
But the book also says,

32:34.070 --> 32:36.270
"use foreign spies to eliminate Li."

32:37.160 --> 32:38.070
Who is this Li?

32:38.070 --> 32:39.350
A distant relative of the Empress Dowager,

32:39.350 --> 32:40.790
Vice Minister of Works, Mr. Li.

32:40.790 --> 32:43.440
So Prince Duan intends to
use someone else's hand to kill

32:43.440 --> 32:44.900
and eliminate his rivals?

32:44.920 --> 32:45.110
So...

32:45.110 --> 32:45.830
So our accidental killing

32:45.830 --> 32:47.630
of the Qiang assassin last night

32:47.680 --> 32:49.590
might have already ruined
Prince Duan's plan.

32:49.590 --> 32:51.270
He might not be from the Qiang State.

32:51.270 --> 32:53.400
Although Qiang also likes to pull tricks,

32:53.400 --> 32:54.790
it's more likely the Yan State's doing.

32:54.790 --> 32:55.240
The Yan State...

32:55.240 --> 32:56.680
Why would the Yan State want to
assassinate someone from Great Xia?

32:56.680 --> 32:58.790
-The Yan State...
-The Yan State wants to fight for power.

32:58.790 --> 33:00.190
Sending a few assassins

33:00.350 --> 33:02.210
to kill key officials of Great Xia

33:02.550 --> 33:05.010
is their bargaining chip
for seizing power.

33:05.720 --> 33:07.180
Plus, the Yan State's land

33:07.200 --> 33:09.400
is barren and plagued by years of drought.

33:09.400 --> 33:10.800
They can barely survive.

33:11.070 --> 33:13.870
The worse their lives get,
the more they resent us.

33:19.350 --> 33:20.550
What's with the "oh"?

33:21.040 --> 33:21.960
Mr. Bei, I'd like to ask,

33:21.960 --> 33:22.450
since

33:22.920 --> 33:24.880
the Yan State's land is dry and barren,

33:24.880 --> 33:26.210
what crops do they grow?

33:26.830 --> 33:29.430
I think it's something called Yan millet.

33:29.920 --> 33:31.110
It's no good anyway,

33:31.110 --> 33:32.510
rough and tastes terrible.

33:32.510 --> 33:34.000
Anyway, we don't grow it here
in Great Xia.

33:34.000 --> 33:36.200
Even if we did, it'd be for feeding pigs.

33:38.790 --> 33:40.570
-I see.
-I see.

33:40.750 --> 33:42.030
Forget about the plans.

33:42.030 --> 33:44.200
I'll just go chop off Prince Duan's head

33:44.200 --> 33:45.600
and save you the trouble.

33:45.760 --> 33:46.240
Mr. Bei!

33:47.200 --> 33:48.720
Prince Duan's faction is deeply rooted.

33:48.720 --> 33:50.200
No matter how good you are, Mr. Bei,

33:50.200 --> 33:51.360
you can't possibly fight thousands alone.

33:51.360 --> 33:51.830
It's fine.

33:51.830 --> 33:52.720
Besides,

33:52.930 --> 33:55.260
Prince Duan is backed by the Three Armies.

33:55.270 --> 33:56.600
Killing him isn't hard.

33:56.960 --> 33:58.880
The hard part is
seizing military power first.

33:58.880 --> 34:00.350
How do we know if we don't try?

34:00.350 --> 34:01.070
-Mr. Bei!
-Mr. Bei!

34:01.070 --> 34:02.470
Even if this is resolved,

34:03.070 --> 34:04.510
the Empress Dowager will reign supreme.

34:04.510 --> 34:05.240
Her next step

34:05.440 --> 34:06.440
will be to kill me.

34:07.070 --> 34:08.320
All this killing back and forth

34:08.320 --> 34:09.400
only treats the symptoms,

34:09.400 --> 34:10.460
not the root cause.

34:10.670 --> 34:12.600
Then how do we treat the root cause?

34:14.760 --> 34:15.889
That depends on her.

34:16.670 --> 34:17.190
Her?

34:17.960 --> 34:20.290
Can a demonic consort really save a state?

34:22.270 --> 34:25.110
[Prince Duan's Mansion]

34:37.880 --> 34:38.630
Your Highness.

34:38.630 --> 34:40.830
Mr. Murong asked me to pass on a message.

34:40.960 --> 34:41.489
Go ahead.

34:42.760 --> 34:44.920
The Commander of the Imperial Guards
indeed has a concubine,

34:44.920 --> 34:46.520
who's extremely beautiful.

34:46.630 --> 34:48.880
She often goes to Nanshan Temple
to burn incense.

34:48.880 --> 34:50.800
Her route and Deputy Commander Zhao's

34:50.800 --> 34:52.130
overlap in some places.

34:52.880 --> 34:54.110
If we drug him

34:54.190 --> 34:55.960
and make him take liberties with her,

34:55.960 --> 34:57.920
the two men will surely become enemies.

34:57.920 --> 35:00.230
If Your Highness recruits
Deputy Commander Zhao then,

35:00.230 --> 35:02.830
you'll surely succeed
in one decisive stroke.

35:05.400 --> 35:06.530
What else did he say?

35:07.030 --> 35:10.400
Mr. Murong praised this plan
for achieving much with little,

35:10.400 --> 35:13.930
and said that the strategist behind it
is worthy of great trust.

35:15.440 --> 35:17.300
Give this letter to His Highness.

35:17.830 --> 35:20.560
It will surely help His Highness
make a comeback.

35:21.320 --> 35:23.470
How does Xie Yong'er know so much?

35:27.150 --> 35:27.930
Your Highness.

35:27.930 --> 35:29.940
Shall I proceed with the plan?

35:31.580 --> 35:32.640
Go and investigate

35:34.030 --> 35:36.000
if Concubine Xie had any dealings
with these people

35:36.000 --> 35:37.730
before she entered the palace.

35:38.550 --> 35:38.980
Yes.

35:55.840 --> 35:56.920
Still reading?

35:57.190 --> 35:58.650
You've been at it for ages.

35:59.800 --> 36:01.480
This is Xu Yao's journal.

36:02.030 --> 36:03.560
He probably never expected

36:03.800 --> 36:05.600
it would become evidence for us.

36:06.510 --> 36:09.280
But a lot of information is hidden
between the lines.

36:09.280 --> 36:10.880
I need to study it carefully.

36:11.710 --> 36:13.280
Study carefully?

36:14.090 --> 36:14.800
Is that so?

36:19.190 --> 36:20.520
Then let me study it too!

36:21.360 --> 36:22.960
I'm not done yet. Stop it.

36:24.150 --> 36:24.840
Xiahou Dan!

36:24.840 --> 36:25.710
Why can't I read it?

36:25.710 --> 36:27.070
You're so childish.

36:27.550 --> 36:28.410
Go take a break.

36:28.840 --> 36:29.430
Stop it.

36:29.670 --> 36:30.670
Give it back to me.

36:30.670 --> 36:32.000
-I'm not done yet.
-Let me study it.

36:32.000 --> 36:33.000
So only you can study it carefully?

36:33.000 --> 36:34.110
Give it to me!

36:36.110 --> 36:37.170
Who allowed you in?

36:37.610 --> 36:39.590
Y-Your Majesty, please forgive me.

36:39.590 --> 36:42.030
These are Her Ladyship's
favorite pastries.

36:42.030 --> 36:43.230
I thought I'd bring them to her...

36:43.230 --> 36:44.550
Leave this sort of thing

36:44.550 --> 36:45.880
to Madam Bei from now on.

36:46.110 --> 36:46.640
Leave us!

36:47.320 --> 36:48.380
Yes, Your Majesty.

36:54.610 --> 36:56.610
You didn't have to be so harsh on her.

36:57.190 --> 36:57.590
Was I?

37:03.320 --> 37:05.190
Look, how do you pronounce this character?

37:04.210 --> 37:06.140
[Talents who failed
the February imperial exam]

37:05.400 --> 37:05.760
Wei.

37:06.590 --> 37:08.990
As in "Weishi," meaning the imperial exam.

37:09.510 --> 37:10.710
Impressive.

37:11.190 --> 37:13.450
You even know such an obscure character.

37:14.360 --> 37:16.560
I picked it up practicing calligraphy.

37:17.110 --> 37:17.670
So here,

37:18.150 --> 37:21.210
"talents who failed
the February imperial exam" means

37:21.440 --> 37:23.360
that during the imperial exam
next February,

37:23.360 --> 37:25.360
Prince Duan will recruit
some of the talents

37:25.360 --> 37:26.760
who fail the exam, right?

37:27.440 --> 37:29.400
Why recruit those who fail?

37:31.110 --> 37:33.570
Because of that Empress Dowager,
of course.

37:33.760 --> 37:35.070
The current imperial exams

37:35.070 --> 37:37.130
are plagued by fraud and corruption.

37:37.710 --> 37:40.510
Scholars from poor families
never stand a chance.

37:40.760 --> 37:43.920
As long as Prince Duan recruits
capable, ambitious people

37:43.920 --> 37:45.670
and offers them even minor official posts,

37:45.670 --> 37:46.670
they'll all end up

37:46.800 --> 37:48.630
pledging their loyalty to him, won't they?

37:48.630 --> 37:49.890
Besides, the book says

37:50.440 --> 37:52.440
the scholars Prince Duan recruited

37:52.630 --> 37:53.830
include many talents

37:54.110 --> 37:55.150
who ended up becoming capable ministers.

37:55.150 --> 37:56.410
What should we do then?

37:58.880 --> 38:00.190
Beat him to it

38:00.840 --> 38:01.700
and poach them.

38:03.880 --> 38:04.540
Poach them?

38:07.510 --> 38:09.710
Your Majesty, I have a matter to report!

38:10.710 --> 38:11.640
I wish to impeach

38:11.950 --> 38:12.910
[Lord Wang]

38:11.990 --> 38:13.040
Minister Yu

38:13.430 --> 38:16.230
for perverting the law
and lining his own pockets.

38:18.510 --> 38:19.480
I second that.

38:20.230 --> 38:22.880
Minister Yu relies on his status
as a royal relative

38:22.880 --> 38:24.540
to disrupt court discipline.

38:24.590 --> 38:26.990
I hope Your Majesty
will judge this fairly.

38:28.030 --> 38:30.520
Although Minister Yu
is Consort Yu's father

38:30.800 --> 38:32.460
and holds a fourth-rank post,

38:32.550 --> 38:33.840
royal relatives

38:34.030 --> 38:36.700
cannot place themselves above the law.

38:40.510 --> 38:41.230
What?

38:58.480 --> 39:01.670
Minister Yu often invites officials
to his residence

39:02.110 --> 39:03.710
and accepts bribes

39:03.880 --> 39:05.740
under the guise of playing cards.

39:05.760 --> 39:07.450
I have recorded all the money

39:07.880 --> 39:10.540
he embezzled in the past year.

39:11.150 --> 39:13.410
I hope Your Majesty prioritizes the law,

39:13.760 --> 39:15.110
handles this impartially,

39:15.110 --> 39:17.370
and does not let Minister Yu off lightly.

39:24.000 --> 39:24.960
How dare you!

39:25.960 --> 39:26.760
Your Majesty!

39:26.880 --> 39:27.590
Your Majesty.

39:27.590 --> 39:28.030
Your Majesty.

39:28.030 --> 39:30.190
Your Majesty, I only have Great Xia's
best interests at heart.

39:30.190 --> 39:31.400
Even if it displeases Your Majesty,

39:31.400 --> 39:31.760
I

39:32.070 --> 39:33.130
must remonstrate!

39:33.760 --> 39:34.940
E-E-Exactly.

39:35.280 --> 39:37.280
I am willing to remonstrate with my life!

39:37.280 --> 39:38.390
So am I!
